<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3775> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3775" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under C. Sentius in Macedonia (IG 9.2.613; an inscription of Thespiae, A. Plassart, Melanges Picard 830- 32; Head, HN² 241, Legatus pro quaestore; Plut. Sull. 11.4; App. Mith. 29; see 93-87, Legates)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3774> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3774" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "7 Bruttius' name is variously spelled: SVVRA on the coins, # in the inseriptions, # in Plut. Sull. 11.4, and # in App. Mith. 29. In Macedonia with Sentius in 88 and 87, and probably from the beginning of his cornmand. See D.-G. 2.559." .
